query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('physics')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('astronomy',
'capacitance',
'charge',
'friction',
'gauge-theory',
'group-theory',
'hamiltonian-formalism',
'heisenberg-uncertainty-principle',
'notation',
'nuclear-physics',
'quantum-spin',
'supersymmetry',
'vectors',
'velocity',
'voltage');
